videos.headline: Moss puts Utes on the board
videos.description: Zack Moss uses his strength and pushes through the pile for a 1-yard touchdown vs. Idaho State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Moss puts Utes on the board) 2019/9/14

videos.headline: Huntley goes deep to Thompson for 82-yard TD
videos.description: Utah QB Tyler Huntley delivers a perfect pass to Bryan Thompson who then takes off running for the end zone for an 82-yard Utes TD.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Huntley goes deep to Thompson for 82-yard TD) 2019/9/14

videos.headline: Utah's Kuithe rushes the sideline for 60-yard TD
